commit 46dc780b1e1b1f28f9d2781798cf8976b2f211e6
Author: Roger Leigh <rleigh@debian.org>
Date:   Fri Dec 30 12:01:15 2011 +0000

    debian: schroot Breaks sbuild << 0.62.6

