commit b91c7c723e885e5e5a85566d1ea7278bb3ab79d8
Author: Roger Leigh <rleigh@debian.org>
Date:   Sun Jan 13 23:46:08 2008 +0000

    * bin/schroot/setup/20network, bin/schroot/setup/30passwd: For files to
