    * Update API reference.

commit 2004c42541e12a6accaccc03b6690ec5ea059302
Author: Roger Leigh <rleigh@debian.org>
Date:   Thu Jun 22 19:13:44 2006 +0000

    * schroot/schroot.1.in, schroot/dchroot.1.in,
