commit a9037df2bb6f4a127cf7863a39a8ed5302ea9f69
Author: Roger Leigh <rleigh@debian.org>
Date:   Fri Apr 7 10:57:41 2006 +0000

    * configure.ac: Bump version to 0.2.9.
    * NEWS: Bump version to 0.2.9.
