    * debian/changelog: Manual pages say "schroot" rather than
      "sbuild".  Closes Debian Bug #331550.
    * schroot/schroot.conf.5.in: Use "schroot" rather than "sbuild".

commit 5f46190c0e1c6f54a7445404c41c8bf1e783dcde
